Once upon a time there lived a Tortoise and a Hare, the hare was very fast and the Tortoise was very slow.
A competition was arranged for the Tortoise and the Hare
the Hare was very fast and reached the middle of the path and looked back at the Tortoise.he found that Tortoise was very slow.
so he thought of sleeping for a while.The tortiose slowly walked while the hare was sleepng and finnaly reached the finish 
the Hare woke up and thought that the tortiose was still behind him and ran towards the finishing line and to his surprise he found out that the tortiose had already won the reached

Moral : Slow and steady wins the  race